Pathao (Bengali: পাঠাও); is a Bangladeshi transportation technology company headquartered in Dhaka, Bangladesh and its operating services in 2 main cities of Bangladesh. Currently it is operating in Dhaka and Chittagong. It operates merchant and Ecommerce Services mobile apps. Pathao riders (drivers) can use their own motorcycle & cars.
Pathao is where you can send things, whether it is a package or yourself to some destination. It has its origins in the Bengali word পাঠাও.
